Food we serve

WINGS & BONELESS

Our wings, with wings we mean real wings with the bone-in are All Natural (with no added hormones). 99% of time our bone-in wings are Halal, but we always recommend you call /ask and reconfirm. That being said our wings are as close to the top of the line product out there.

We do offer different texture for the wings

Regular = Nice and juicy yet crispy.

Xtra crispy = Crispy Less juicy

Xtra Xtra crispy = Super crispy = Very very dry and no juice left (people who order these come back again and again for these, but again it’s not for everyone.)

*** Please note if you are very particular about your wings being crispy, we recommend you dine-in. Or get wings naked with sauce on the side.

Boneless chicken, is not wings and even worldwide, most likely is never is. Here at IWF we fabricate and make our own boneless from chicken breast and chicken tenders. Our boneless is NOT factory processed meat, NOR is it BREADED. However we use a light batter so that the chicken doesn’t dry. The batter that we use is gluten free too.

So if you are used to enjoying the heavily breaded boneless which they call “Boneless WINGS” then we would recommend stay away from our Boneless.

Our boneless is extremely popular but to enjoy our boneless you have to be open minded and accepting that it is nontraditional.  And you can appreciate the hard labor that goes into making them in-house.

SANDWICHES & BURGERS

All Sandwiches and Burgers come with a small regular fries. You can upgrade to sweet potato fries, add that extra cheese or Bacon for an upcharge.

IWF Glazed Cheese Burger

 IWF stands for “International Wings Factory and NOT “International Wrestling Federation”. Sorry we had to put this one here, as many people come and ask us what does IWF stands for.  This is a 5.5 to  6oz burger 100% Angus beef & American Cheese on a Brioche bun with homemade magic relish mayo dressing spread, salad greens, glaze of any sauce from the menu, tomato and pickles. This burger is done on a pan comes out nice juicy and delicious

B.C.T SANDwICH

Our Bacon Cucumber Ranch and Tomato Sandwich is one of the real crowd pleaser. It is messy as hell, loaded with flavor. This sandwich is made with fried chicken tenders, tossed in Buffalo sauce served on a Brioche, with our relish mayo spread, cucumber, bacon and tomato.

BBQ Chicken Sandwich

BBQ lover’s delight. This sandwich is made with fried chicken tenders, tossed in BBQ sauce served on a Brioche roll, with our relish mayo spread, creamy red cabbage coleslaw, chipotle mayo drizzle, Pepper jack cheese and tomato.

Fire Chicken Sandwich

 Simply Hot and flavorful, This sandwich is made with fried chicken tenders, tossed in our house blended chili sauce and chili oil, served on a Brioche roll, with our relish mayo spread, Cheese and tomato.

Blackened Spiced Chicken Sandwich 

This Cajun spice inspired chicken sandwich is the ONLY non- fried chicken that we serve here. It is served on a Brioche roll, with Chipotle mayo spread, creamy Red cabbage coleslaw, American cheese and Tomato.

Crispy Tilapia Sandwich

This is so popular that we call it “chicken of the sea popular”. This large filet is lightly dredged in our special blend of flour and fried, served on a Brioche roll with Chipotle mayo spread, salad greens, pepper jack cheese and tomato.

Chunky Vegetable burger

Mixed chunky vegetable patty & American Cheese on a Brioche bun with homemade magic relish mayo dressing spread, salad greens, tomato and pickles. This burger is done on a pan comes out nice juicy and delicious. This is a burger where you can see the vegetables you are eating not just another mush.

FRIES & SIDES

Regular fries

These are Skin On fries, layered with More like fresh cut fries, but we don’t cut them on premises. They are brined, so they naturally have salt in them. But we do offer 4 different season blend to enhance their flavor.

Sweet Potato fries

These are awesome platter cut fries, They come out nice and crispy. But if you ask us to make it crispier it might get darker as we cook them longer. Since the sugar content in sweet potato fries changes. We do offer 4 different season blend to enhance their flavor.


Sriracha Hinted Cheesy Fries

These are Skin On fries over some melted Sriracha cheese sauce, layered with more cheese (3 different types) topped hot Sriracha hinted cheese sauce, scallions and southwestern season blend.

Please note: For delivery, we give a 2oz cup of cheese sauce on the side by default. Unless specified to have it topped with cheese sauce. Or just specify in your order “Make it nice and messy”.

Battered Onion rings

These are thick sliced rings from Onions, then batter fried. We do offer 4 different season blend to enhance their flavor.

Cheesy Red Onion rings

These are thick sliced rings from Red Onions, then batter fried. Rest over some melted cheese sauce, layered with more cheese (3 different types) topped hot cheese sauce, scallions and southwestern season blend.

We do offer 4 different season blend to enhance their flavor

Please note: For delivery, we give a 2oz cup of cheese sauce on the side by default. Unless specified to have it topped with cheese sauce. Or just specify in your order “Make it nice and messy”.

Chipotle Cinnamon Rice and Beans

Simple dish done with elegance with unmatched flavors. Lot of bold flavors. Served in a 8oz cup, enough for one person.


Mac N Mozz

Nothing fancy, but super cheesy bursting with flavor from 4 different cheeses, Cheddar, Monterey Jack, Provolone and a whole LOT of Mozzarella. People can’t have enough of it

Served in a 8oz cup, enough for one person.

Garlic Red Skin Mashed Potato

It is as simple as the name says it. It is homemade, creamy, garlicky and buttery mash and No we don’t serve it with gravy. Served in a 8oz cup, enough for one person.

Battered Mozzarella sticks

Brined and battered stringy goodness served with Marinara sauce.

Vegan Soy Nuggets

These soy nuggets are breaded and deep fried. You can choose any sauce to be quoted on them.

Red Cabbage Creamy Coleslaw

Served in about 5 to 6oz portions generally enough for just one person. It made with brined red cabbage only.


Caesar salad

Served 3 ways : Plain OR topped with Buffalo Chicken chunks OR Fried Tilapia. Romaine is tossed in our house blended dressing with croutons. Our dressing has bit of anchovy paste. Drizzled with Ranch.

Brownies

Not just any brownie, it is panko crusted and deep fried. Served with jhomemade chipote mixed berries compote.
